OL,3,CSouth East Water outage: Why is this
OL,4,Chappening and what areas are affected?
OL,6,FA major incident has been declared as
OL,7,Fthousands of properties in Kent and
OL,8,FSussex are without a proper water
OL,9,Fsupply.
OL,11,FSouth East Water (SEW) has apologised
OL,12,Fto those affected, saying its repair
OL,13,Fteams are working "around the clock"
OL,14,Fto restore supplies, though it remains
OL,15,Funclear when normal services will
OL,16,Fresume.
OL,18,FSo why is this happening, and which
OL,19,Fareas are affected? ITV News explains.
OL,21,FWhy is it happening?
