OL,3,CSouth East Water outage: Why is this
OL,4,Chappening and what areas are affected?
OL,6,FSEW said the outage was caused by
OL,7,Frecent weather, with freeze-thaw
OL,8,Fconditions leading to burst pipes and
OL,9,Flow drinking water supplies.
OL,11,FThe company also blamed Storm Goretti
OL,12,Flast week, which affected its ability
OL,13,Fto treat raw water at its normal rate.
OL,15,FAdditionally, SEW said it has not
OL,16,Freceived a consistent bulk supply of
OL,17,Fwater from a neighbouring company, as
OL,18,Fit normally would.
