OL,3,CSouth East Water outage: Why is this
OL,4,Chappening and what areas are affected?
OL,6,F"Following the recent cold weather and
OL,7,Fa subsequent breakout of leaks and
OL,8,Fbursts across Kent and Sussex, our
OL,9,Fdrinking water storage tanks are
OL,10,Frunning very low, and there are
OL,11,Fcurrently around 30,000 impacted
OL,12,Fproperties across the two counties,"
OL,13,FIncident Manager Matthew Dean said on
OL,14,FMonday.
OL,16,FIs this a recurring issue for South
OL,17,FEast Water?
OL,19,FYes. This is the second time in two
OL,20,Fmonths that households in South East
OL,21,FEngland have faced water shortages.
