OL,3,CSouth East Water outage: Why is this
OL,4,Chappening and what areas are affected?
OL,6,FIn December 2025, around 24,000 people
OL,7,Fin Tunbridge Wells experienced supply
OL,8,Fproblems.
OL,10,FWhat do regulators and politicians say?
OL,12,FWater regulator Ofwat has expressed
OL,13,Fconcern over the situation and said it
OL,14,Fis actively investigating SEW's
OL,15,F"supply resilience."
OL,17,FMP Helen Grant, representing Maidstone
OL,18,Fand Malling, said SEW "must not be
OL,19,Fallowed to get away with their latest
OL,20,Fhandling of another water crisis".
