OL,3,CSouth East Water outage: Why is this
OL,4,Chappening and what areas are affected?
OL,6,FGrant is among several MPs calling for
OL,7,FSEW's chief executive, David Hinton,
OL,8,Fto resign.
OL,10,FSpeaking in the House of Commons
OL,11,Fyesterday, Lib Dem MP for Tunbridge
OL,12,FWells, Mike Martin, criticised the
OL,13,Fcompany's leadership.
OL,15,FSEW was also fined #3.2 million in
OL,16,F2022-23 by Ofwat for supply failures
OL,17,Fand has faced penalties for repeated
OL,18,Funderperformance in service delivery,
OL,19,Fincluding supply interruptions.
